msgctxt "92_Kiryu"
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr "¿Quién eres?"

msgctxt "104_???"
msgid "I'm with the Purple Killers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116_???"
msgid "I hear you've been having some fun with my men."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128_Kiryu"
msgid "I take it you're the boss? Just what are you planning, anyway?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140_Purple Killers Boss"
msgid "Oh, I was just thinking about all the things I could do to you."
msgstr "Oh, Estaba pensando en todas las cosas que podría hacerte."

msgctxt "152_Kiryu"
msgid "Save your delusional fantasies for later. Let's settle this once and for all. My questions can wait till after I kick your ass."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164_Purple Killers Boss"
msgid "Well. You're rather bullheaded, aren't you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "176_Purple Killers Boss"
msgid "I've seen many who run in fear from a killer, but running towards one is something new."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "188_Purple Killers Boss"
msgid "You're not even going to bother asking how I got your phone number?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "200_Purple Killers Boss"
msgid "I'm rather excited about this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "212_Purple Killers Boss"
msgid "I'll tell you what. How about we meet at the bowling alley?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "224_Kiryu"
msgid "The bowling alley? Got it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "236_Purple Killers Boss"
msgid "Just watch yourself. My men have been ordered to kill you on sight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "248_Purple Killers Boss"
msgid "Careful you don't end up in a ditch on the way over here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "260_Kiryu"
msgid "Hmph. You wish."
